name: The Travel Planet
overview:
Welcome to Travel Planet India!!! Travel Planet India is a premier travel company offering inbound travel services especially in South India. All the members of the company are absolutely passionate about providing you a best holiday in India and we are expert in making tour itineraries to suit individuals, group of people and we aim to develop and provide innovative and competent services to our clients.

We have a team of dedicated professionals striving hard to provide excellent tour in terms of tour planning, cost, hotels suggestions, transportations, tourism information, sightseeing, shopping, multilingual guide, special interest tours and rail tickets bookings.

Please go through the website and send us your holiday requirement and we will look after you with pleasure.

We look forward to welcoming you in the most enchanting country in the world
